# Intelligent Test Architecture - Playwright + TypeScript

> Modern Test Automation Architecture using Playwright and TypeScript.

---

# Objective

This project provides a scalable architecture for Quality Engineering using **Playwright + TypeScript**.

The initial focus is **Web UI automation**, but the architecture is prepared to evolve to:

- Web UI
- API Testing
- Integration Testing
- Contract Testing
- Component Testing
- Performance Support
- CI/CD
- Observability
- AI Assisted Testing

