# Creating the project

## Create folder

```bash
mkdir intelligent-test-architecture-playwright-typescript

cd intelligent-test-architecture-playwright-typescript
```

---

## Initialize Node

```bash
npm init -y
```

---

## Install Playwright

```bash
npm install -D @playwright/test typescript @types/node
```

---

## Install browsers

```bash
npx playwright install
```

or

```bash
npx playwright install chromium
```

---

## Install dotenv

```bash
npm install dotenv
```

---

## Create TypeScript configuration

```bash
npx tsc --init
```

---

## Create folders

```bash
mkdir -p src/pages
mkdir -p src/flows
mkdir -p src/components
mkdir -p src/assertions
mkdir -p src/fixtures
mkdir -p src/data
mkdir -p src/config
mkdir -p src/utils
mkdir -p src/types

mkdir -p tests/web
mkdir -p tests/api

mkdir docs
```

---

## Create base files

```bash
touch playwright.config.ts

touch README.md

touch .env.example

touch .env.local

touch .gitignore

touch src/pages/LoginPage.ts

touch src/flows/LoginFlow.ts

touch src/assertions/LoginAssertions.ts

touch src/fixtures/testFixtures.ts

touch src/data/users.ts

touch src/config/environment.ts

touch src/types/environment.types.ts

touch tests/web/login.spec.ts
```

---

# package.json scripts

```json
{
  "scripts": {

    "test":"playwright test",

    "test:web":"playwright test --project=web-chromium",

    "test:api":"playwright test --project=api",

    "test:headed":"playwright test --project=web-chromium --headed",

    "test:debug":"playwright test --project=web-chromium --debug",

    "test:ui":"playwright test --ui",

    "test:list":"playwright test --list",

    "report":"playwright show-report",

    "typecheck":"tsc --noEmit"

  }
}
```

